Sí, gracias.

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:39.581
Cuida al viejo, ¿sí?

00:16:39.665 --> 00:16:40.833
Claro. Nos vemos.

00:16:41.250 --> 00:16:42.251
Adiós.

00:16:44.420 --> 00:16:46.130
